# Bandit Level 0 Write-Up

## Lesson
How to connect remotely to a server using SSH with a custom port. Simple in hindsight, but tricky the first time!

## Reflections
This level proved challenging despite clear instructions. I struggled to determine where to place the username, assuming it would prompt me like a password. It took trial and error to realize the correct approach with the remote access tool, a valuable lesson in attention to detail.

## Conclusion
Moving forward, I’ll focus more closely on instructions. The secret often lies in the subtle in-line details—patience is key!

